Greetings of Fortitude, Excellence, and Uprightness!🔰� 
We are 4th-year BS Psychology students from Far Eastern University-Manila and we are in search of participants!

“A Correlational and Comparative Study of Self-Silencing in Filipino Men's Romantic Relationships”

We are looking for Filipino men in a romantic relationship with any of the following statuses:
👩‍❤️‍👨Dating but not cohabiting
🏠Cohabiting
💍Married 

Your participation will help us understand how relationship length and status affect self-silencing behaviors. 

You may scan the QR code or click the link below to join:
https://forms.gle/YrxnYvowkH534ggq7
https://forms.gle/YrxnYvowkH534ggq7
https://forms.gle/YrxnYvowkH534ggq7

📞If there are any inquiries, You may contact:
Allyza Joy R. Baidowi
2022072471@feu.edu.ph
09474884357

Thank you for lending your voice—even in silence 😌

Greetings of Fortitude, Excellence, and Uprightness!🔰� 
We are 4th-year BS Psychology students from Far Eastern University-Manila and we are in search of participants!

“A Correlational and Comparative Study of Self-Silencing in Filipino Men's Romantic Relationships”

We are looking for Filipino men in a romantic relationship with any of the following statuses:
👩‍❤️‍👨Dating but not cohabiting
🏠Cohabiting
💍Married 

Your participation will help us understand how relationship length and status affect self-silencing behaviors. 

You may scan the QR code or click the link below to join:
https://forms.gle/YrxnYvowkH534ggq7
https://forms.gle/YrxnYvowkH534ggq7
https://forms.gle/YrxnYvowkH534ggq7

📞If there are any inquiries, You may contact:
Allyza Joy R. Baidowi
2022072471@feu.edu.ph
09474884357

Thank you for lending your voice—even in silence 😌
